title: Ben Folds-The Best Imitation Of Myself:A Retrospective-MP3/320
description:
Ben Folds - The Best Imitation Of Myself: A Retrospective (2011)

This is not a Greatest Hits compilation, many tracks are live, extended versions, or variations on the original studio recording. There are several covers as well.
